# HARD CONSTRAINTS v8 (NEVER VIOLATE — 51 RULES)

## Core
1. Single HTML file. No external files. No imports.
2. Zero external dependencies. No CDN. No frameworks. No Google Fonts.
3. Mobile-first: 80%+ traffic is mobile on 3G/4G.
4. Page weight < 500KB (excluding images).
5. `direction: rtl` on `<html>`. `lang="ar"`.
6. Order form IS the only conversion point. No external links except WhatsApp.
7. All editable text marked `<!-- [EDITABLE: LABEL] -->`.
8. Form data POSTed to GAS_URL via fetch with `mode: 'no-cors'`.
9. Countdown backed by localStorage — never resets on refresh.
10. Honeypot field checked FIRST.

## Pricing & Trust
11. **NEVER** write "توصيل مجاني" anywhere.
12. **NEVER** show a shipping price anywhere on the page.
13. Size AND Color REQUIRED before form submit — shake animation if missing.
14. Order summary shows ONLY product price — no shipping math.
15. Bundle pricing cards MUST show savings amount prominently.
16. "Stop Desk" option MUST clarify office pickup (للاستلام من المكتب).
17. **NEVER** promise specific COD amount during confirmation — only post-call.

## Algerian Specific
18. 69 wilayas + 1,541 communes cascade.
19. Wilaya 59-69 follow Loi 26-06 order.
20. ALL CTA text uses gender-aware Arabic (feminine "اطلبي"/masculine "اطلب"/neutral "اشتري").
21. Phone validation: `^(05|06|07)[0-9]{8}$` only.
22. Commune entries NO non-Arabic characters.

## Layout & UX
23. Hero section MUST fit 100vh on mobile.
24. ALL tap targets minimum 44×44px with 8px gap between targets.
25. Form wizard on mobile (<768px): 3 steps.
26. Sticky price bar (mobile only) above trust bar.
27. WhatsApp floating button: 52px circle, above sticky bar on mobile.

## Animation & A11y
28. Only animate `transform` & `opacity` (GPU-accelerated).
29. ALL animations disabled under `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce`.
30. Respect `prefers-contrast: more`.
31. `:focus-visible` rings only on keyboard navigation.
32. RTL-aware scroll & parallax.
33. ARIA labels on all interactive elements (`aria-live` for toasts/errors).

## Data & State
34. Form draft auto-save to localStorage every 3s.
35. localStorage form draft restore on load (with reset button).
36. Submit cooldown: 30s lockout after first attempt (anti-double).
37. Browser back button after submit → confirmation state restored.

## SEO & Tracking
38. Open Graph + Twitter Card meta tags.
39. Product schema (`schema.org/Product`) with `Offer` and `AggregateRating`.
40. FAQ schema for accordion section.
41. Organization schema for BRAND_NAME.
42. UTM parameters captured and stored in hidden fields before submit.

## Dark Patterns — AVOID
43. **NO** fake urgency "only 1 left!" unless backed by real inventory data.
44. **NO** countdown that resets on refresh (use localStorage duration).
45. **NO** smooth-scroll hijacking that traps the user.
46. **NO** modal that cannot be closed without action.

## File & Code Quality
47. No unused CSS rules.
48. No console.log noise.
49. No inline styles except in dynamically generated content.
50. All event listeners use passive flag where applicable.
51. Use semantic HTML5 elements throughout.

