# v8.0 ANIMATION SYSTEM — CINEMATIC

## A. Entrance Patterns (IO-triggered)

```css
/* FADE UP — base reveal */
.reveal-fade { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px);
  transition: opacity .8s var(--ease-out-expo), transform .8s var(--ease-out-expo); }
.reveal-fade.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

/* FADE UP STAGGER */
.reveal-stagger > * { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity .6s var(--ease-out-expo), transform .6s var(--ease-out-expo); }
.reveal-stagger.visible > *              { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
