# FINAL NOTES

Build pages that feel **editorially designed**, not template-made. Every section should justify its layout. Every animation should feel intentional, not decorative.

The target user is a **real Algerian shopper**, on a **mid-range Android on 3G/4G**, browsing during a **work break**, in **RTL Arabic**, possibly **mixed with French/English characters**. She's 5 seconds away from leaving. Make those 5 seconds feel premium, trusted, and effortless.

When done well, the page doesn't feel like e-commerce — it feels like a boutique experience that happens to have a checkout built into the story.

